418
01:44:59,585 --> 01:45:02,296
Pardon, Wilson.

419
01:47:23,270 --> 01:47:25,147
Comment vas-tu ?

420
01:47:50,464 --> 01:47:53,676
Quatre semaines plus tard

421
01:48:09,358 --> 01:48:10,943
45 minutes.

422
01:48:12,444 --> 01:48:14,071
Un Dr Pepper.

423
01:48:15,280 --> 01:48:16,865
Deux gobelets de glaçons.

424
01:48:17,574 --> 01:48:19,159
J'adore les glaçons.

425
01:48:22,871 --> 01:48:24,164
Voilà le programme.

426
01:48:25,082 --> 01:48:26,875
L'avion se pose, on descend

427
01:48:27,251 --> 01:48:30,671
